Package com.google.genkit.core

Enum Class ActionType

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<ActionType>
com.google.genkit.core.ActionType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<ActionType>, Constable
public enum ActionType extends Enum<ActionType>
ActionType represents the kind of an action. Each type corresponds to a different Genkit primitive or capability.
